I think the real issue here is that sourceQuery is expecting a list when it should expect a singular value.
The input field was a "select" list in QuickStart with a typeahead showing existing collections in STAGING. For HubCentral I think we decided not to provide type ahead and go with 1 collection.
@rjrudin  @xnikhil08 please correct me if I am wrong.

